title: A Connecticut Yankee goes to Washington: Senator George P. McLean, Birdman of the Senate
content: A Connecticut Yankee goes to Washington: Senator George P. McLean, Birdman of the Senate. by GreeleyWill McLean. 2023. RIT Press, Rochester, New York. pp., 21 Black-and-White Illustrations. $34.95 (softcover). ISBN 978-1-939125-99-6.
